{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 26.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I had some Mennen's shave lotion that I-- that my wife had sent me or somebody had sent me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I can remember putting that damn Mennen shaving lotion, that green stuff, gargling with it and spitting it out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it tasted like hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I was just putting that all over me, you know, my hair and all over my shirt, between my toes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had G.I. foot powder for not athlete's foot, for trench foot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Then we always put that inside of our socks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I'm putting all that stuff in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I-- I went back in the camp two or three more times because I just had to do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, and we talked about the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I told you that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The-- the-- there was an execution chamber, a wall where-- it had-- it had been a firing range.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they had set it up as the execution wall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they would-- they would take thousands in a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They would execute 1,500, 2,000 men, Russians, Russian POWs, for example.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "All the Russian POWs were killed in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They didn't-- and then Himmler heard about this and said, now, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I read this in a book too, something I just got yesterday, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That he felt that if things were getting too hairy, they better stop this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they started evac-- well, they had already started evacuating the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had evacuated Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had tried to evacuate Buchenwald before we got there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had evacuated a lot of men from Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most of them had been killed or died en route.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't-- and like the train had been shuttled back and forth to different camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody would take the train, accept it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
